data.description: This beautiful home built in 2013 has 3 bedroom, 2 full bath and a 2 car garage. Located 20 minutes from Ft. Cavazos and all amenities within a 5 mile radius including shopping centers, restaurants, medical and entertainment. As you step into this inviting home, you are immediately greeted by a welcoming and spacious living room that exudes comfort and style.The thoughtful design of this home includes a designated wing exclusively reserved for two bedrooms and a full bath. This home features a practical full bathroom complete with a bathtub, providing a simple yet comfortable space for daily routines. Completing the layout on the opposite side of the designated wing is the generously sized master bedroom. The master ensuite is designed for both functionality and personal space, featuring a thoughtful separation between the shower and bathtub areas. This arrangement allows for versatile and efficient use of the bathroom space.The separate closets not only provide ample storage but also cater to individual organizational. Adding to the convenience and practicality of this home is a spacious laundry room strategically located right outside the master bedroom. The spaciousness of the laundry room provides ample room for laundry appliances, storage, and additional organizational  Features. With closet space in close proximity, residents can seamlessly transition between the laundry area and the master bedroom, creating a functional and integrated living space. This home boasts a good-sized kitchen, striking a balance between spaciousness and practicality. The well-proportioned layout provides ample room for meal preparation, cooking, and socializing. This home is designed to offer a seamless flow from the kitchen to the covered patio, extending into a generously sized backyard.
